title: Unemployment rate in Cambodia 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Unemployment rate, containing a total of 21 data points.
In general Unemployment rate has fallen over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2000 and 2001.
Maximum Unemployment rate, about 2.55 was reported at Year 1999
The lowest Unemployment rate, of value 1.02 was reported at Year 2019
